1195
02:00:06,208 --> 02:00:07,416
Pilote et tais-toi.

1196
02:00:08,208 --> 02:00:09,541
Où est le blé ?

1197
02:00:10,458 --> 02:00:11,541
Oublie le blé.

1198
02:00:12,041 --> 02:00:15,333
Mais Peters,
Kate est à l'Olympus. On va la chercher.

1199
02:00:17,458 --> 02:00:18,958
